1. At the beginning of the game, one of the 4 buttons lights up randomly
        producing simultaneously a sound associated to the button. <br />2.
        Player has to press the same button. <br />3. Next, another button
        lights up randomly. <br />4. Player has to reproduce this chain of
        button light from beginning using his memory. <br />5. Score level is
        increased each time when player reproduces the chain of light
        successfully
